  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together lemon juice, olive oil, garlic, and turmeric.",
    "Add the chicken to the bowl and marinate for at least 10 minutes.",
    "Place the flatbread pieces on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Top each flatbread piece with a piece of chicken, some green olives, and a sprinkle of feta cheese.",
    "Bake the flatbreads in the preheated oven for 15 minutes or until the chicken is cooked through.",
    "Remove the flatbreads from the oven and let them cool for a few minutes.",
    "Serve the flatbreads hot and enjoy."
  ],
